The evidence with the title 'Air pollution and asthma | aafa.org ' says Studies have shown that air pollution is related to the worsening of asthma symptoms .  ... 40 percent more likely to have acute asthma episodes on high pollution summer days than on days  ... Ozone can make it more difficult for you to breathe deeply .  ... When the AQI is 101 or higher , it is dangerous for people with asthma . 
